      <p>Yanagida (2006) analyzes the properties of adnominal clauses as in (47):</p>
      <p>Case and argument realization in OJ
(i) Ga-marked subjects stay in the base external argument position
(Spec, vP).
(ii) Bare objects are incorporated into the verb.
